How’s it going?

00:07:09.960 --> 00:07:11.260
I found Jett.

00:07:12.590 --> 00:07:13.430
Where is he?

00:07:15.430 --> 00:07:16.700
He’s at the Hunters’ secret base.

00:07:49.860 --> 00:07:50.870
Mr. Ramil.

00:07:54.460 --> 00:07:55.930
How are you going to help Jett?

00:07:56.540 --> 00:07:59.409
