Don’t worry, Elise.

00:17:34.900 --> 00:17:36.220
I’ll bring Jett back.

00:17:36.990 --> 00:17:38.990
You must come back to me too.

00:17:45.010 --> 00:17:45.720
Hey.

00:17:57.200 --> 00:17:58.060
Feratu!

00:17:59.340 --> 00:18:00.010
Jett!

00:18:05.840 --> 00:18:06.460
Jett!

00:18:07.180 --> 00:18:07.880
Jett!

00:18:12.360 --> 00:18:13.060
Punn!

00:18:16.570 --> 00:18:17.620
Stop it, Feratu!

00:18:22.320 --> 00:18:25.180
If I survive, I’ll hunt that boy of yours down.

00:18:27.230 --> 00:18:29.180
There won’t be a next time, Feratu.

00:18:43.530 --> 00:18:44.180
Jett!

00:18:44.620 --> 00:18:45.360
Jett!

00:18:46.520 --> 00:18:47.160
Jett!

00:18:47.640 --> 00:18:48.940
Wake up, Jett!

00:19:05.770 --> 00:19:09.100
May the three of us grow up together.

00:19:10.430 --> 00:19:13.070
May we stay together forever.

